  m_Name: Step_2_HoiSanPham
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionStep
  questionText: "Ch\u1ECDn lo\u1EA1i b\xE1nh m\xEC \u0111\u1EC3 b\xE1n:"
  optionA:
    text: "A. B\xE1nh m\xEC d\xE1t v\xE0ng 24K (Gi\xE1 500k/c\xE1i) cho sang ch\u1EA3nh."
    capitalChange: -2000000
    brandChange: -10
    techChange: 0
    feedback: "L\u1ED7 v\u1ED1n! Sinh vi\xEAn kh\xF4ng c\xF3 ti\u1EC1n mua. H\xE0ng
      h\xF3a ph\u1EA3i c\xF3 gi\xE1 tr\u1ECB s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng th\u1ECFa m\xE3n nhu
      c\u1EA7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi mua, nh\u01B0ng ph\u1EA3i ph\xF9 h\u1EE3p v\u1EDBi
      kh\u1EA3 n\u0103ng thanh to\xE1n."
  optionB:
    text: "B. B\xE1nh m\xEC kh\xF4ng kh\xED (v\u1ECF kh\xF4ng ru\u1ED9t) cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
      gi\u1EA3m c\xE2n."
    capitalChange: -5000000
    brandChange: -50
    techChange: 0
    feedback: "Ph\xE1 s\u1EA3n! Kh\xF4ng ai mua. H\xE0ng h\xF3a l\xE0 s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m
      c\u1EE7a lao \u0111\u1ED9ng, v\u1ECF r\u1ED7ng kh\xF4ng \u0111\xE1p \u1EE9ng
      nhu c\u1EA7u \u0103n no (Gi\xE1 tr\u1ECB s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng th\u1EA5p)."
  optionC:
    text: "C. B\xE1nh m\xEC tr\u1EE9ng x\xFAc x\xEDch (Gi\xE1 15k/c\xE1i) \u0111\u1EA7y
      \u0111\u1EB7n, n\xF3ng h\u1ED5i."
    capitalChange: 1000000
    brandChange: 20
    techChange: 5
    feedback: "Ch\xEDnh x\xE1c! H\xE0ng h\xF3a l\xE0 s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m c\u1EE7a
      lao \u0111\u1ED9ng c\xF3 th\u1EC3 th\u1ECFa m\xE3n nhu c\u1EA7u n\xE0o \u0111\xF3
      c\u1EE7a con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi th\xF4ng qua trao \u0111\u1ED5i, mua b\xE1n. Sinh
      vi\xEAn c\u1EA7n \u0103n no v\xE0 gi\xE1 r\u1EBB, \u0111\xE2y l\xE0 'Gi\xE1
      tr\u1ECB s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng' thi\u1EBFt th\u1EF1c nh\u1EA5t.\\n\\n(Th\u01B0\u1EDFng:
      +1.000.000 VN\u0110)"
